{"tid":512421,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"\"亂扣帽子\"一詞唔算係匪語","createTime":"2017-12-28T12:47:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-29T03:06:26.000Z","uid":143499,"like":5,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"05fe855c01bcb9cc4bda26f89ca861e4d8c91dfd","tid":512421,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T12:47:54.000Z","msg":"我認為所謂嘅匪語應該係將普通詞語惡意簡化扭曲/ 中文歐化/ 大陸譯音<br />\n<br />\n但係亂扣帽子一詞係來自文化大革命, 形容被批鬥對象須戴上寫有罪名嘅高帽, 即係砌人生豬肉咁嘅意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢個字雖然出自共產黨嘅產品, 但係純粹 反應獨特歷史現像，毫無扭曲中文。<br />\n<br />\n如果呢個字都係匪語, 咁五毛呢個字都係匪語，因為出自大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaee9fc998adcfb2473eddbab33e4275ba22217d","tid":512421,"uid":143499,"like":6,"dislike":20,"score":-14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T12:48:55.000Z","msg":"大家評下理<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 唔係匪語<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 係匪語"},{"pid":"a0abbd2e9f7aa58e8bd61f1ea4d4a9430588e287","tid":512421,"uid":52194,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T12:50:03.000Z","msg":"除左大陸真心無咩地方聽過<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a431ce579f1fbdac1d33f40084afe99f742f746","tid":512421,"uid":147022,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T12:50:33.000Z","msg":"係又點唔係又點？你同你朋友拗緊所以上嚟開post投票？"},{"pid":"1b23606814a07888909a6fa705f1b1485e722869","tid":512421,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"a0abbd2e9f7aa58e8bd61f1ea4d4a9430588e287","tid":512421,"uid":52194,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T12:50:03.000Z","msg":"除左大陸真心無咩地方聽過<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T12:51:12.000Z","msg":"但係佢唔符合匪嘅定義<br />\n<br />\n唔同伊斯坦布爾，打造優化呢啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d899895a04a348